lyric:
[00:00.000] 作曲 : Tamas Wells
[00:00.233] 作词 : Tamas Wells
[00:00.700]I was found on the ground by the fountain at valder
[00:07.300]fields and was almost dry
[00:09.700]lying in the sun after I had tried
[00:13.700]lying in the sun by the side
[00:20.700]We had agreed that the council would end at
[00:25.340]three hours over time
[00:27.700]shoelaces were tied at the traffic lights
[00:31.700]I was running late I could apply
[00:38.000]For another one I guess
[00:43.000]If department stores are best
[00:47.000]They said there would be delays and
[00:51.000]only temporary pay
[01:34.000]For another one I guess
[01:38.000]If department stores are best
[01:42.000]They said there would be delays and
[01:46.650]only temporary pay
[01:51.000]She was found on the ground in a gown made at valder
[01:58.900]fields and was sound asleep
[02:00.300]on the stairs outside the door to the man who cried
[02:05.300]when he said that he loved his life
[02:12.300]We had agreed that the council should take his
[02:16.540]keys to the bedroom door
[02:19.300]incase he sleeped outside and was found in two
[02:23.300]days in valder fields with a mountain view
tlyric:
[00:00.700]我躺在泉边的地上就在瓦尔德
[00:07.300]的田野里，快被晒干了
[00:09.700]挣扎之后躺在烈日下面
[00:13.700]躺在那里躺在烈日旁边
[00:20.700]我们已经决定委员会将解散于
[00:25.340]三个小时之后
[00:27.700]在红绿灯前系了鞋带
[00:31.700]但我还是没赶上，我还可以申请
[00:38.000]别的工作吧，试试吧
[00:43.000]如果是商场那就最好不过了
[00:47.000]他们说先干活后拿钱而且
[00:51.000]这不是一个长久的差事
[01:34.000]别的工作吧，试试吧
[01:38.000]如果是商场那就最好不过了
[01:42.000]他们说先干活后拿钱而且
[01:46.650]这不是一个长久的差事
[01:51.000]她躺在地上，穿着的礼服来自瓦尔德
[01:58.900]乡间，她很安稳地睡
[02:00.300]在门外的楼梯上，在那个男人面前
[02:05.300]那个一提到他其实热爱生活就泪流满面的男人
[02:12.300]我们已经决定委员会将拿走他
[02:16.540]卧室的门钥匙
[02:19.300]既然他已经在外面睡了两
[02:23.300]天，睡在瓦尔德田野的山色间
